imdb.plot outline: Perform a top-secret reno for one unsuspecting homeowner while they toil away at their 9-5 job. Nominated by their spouse, family or housemate, the unknowing party thinks it is literally "just another day at the office". Little do they know that they are about to receive an incredible makeover in one major area of their house.
